OL,3,CBarry Manilow says he is undergoing
OL,4,Csurgery after 'early' lung cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FSinger Barry Manilow has revealed he
OL,8,Fhas a cancerous spot on his lung and
OL,9,Fwill undergo surgery.
OL,11,FThe 82-year-old musician shared the
OL,12,Fnews on Monday, revealing that he was
OL,13,Fpostponing a string of upcoming
OL,14,Fconcerts due to his diagnosis.
OL,16,FHe said that he was diagnosed with
OL,17,Flung cancer after his doctor
OL,18,Frecommended he undergo an MRI scan
OL,19,Ffollowing an 11-week bout of
OL,20,Fbronchitis.
