OL,7,FIn a post shared to his Instagram
OL,8,Faccount, he said: "As many of you know
OL,9,FI recently went through six weeks of
OL,10,Fbronchitis followed by a relapse of
OL,11,Fanother five weeks.
OL,13,F"Even though I was over the bronchitis
OL,14,Fand back on stage at the Westgate Las
OL,15,FVegas, my wonderful doctor ordered an
OL,16,FMRI just to make sure that everything
OL,17,Fwas OK.
