OL,3,CBarry Manilow says he is undergoing
OL,4,Csurgery after 'early' lung cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,F"The MRI discovered a cancerous spot
OL,8,Fon my left lung that needs to be
OL,9,Fremoved. It's pure luck (and a great
OL,10,Fdoctor) that it was found so early.
OL,11,FThat's the good news.
OL,13,FHe continued: "The bad news is that
OL,14,Fnow that the Christmas Gift Of Love
OL,15,Fconcerts are over I'm going into
OL,16,Fsurgery to have the spot removed.
