OL,3,CBarry Manilow says he is undergoing
OL,4,Csurgery after 'early' lung cancer
OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,F"The doctors do not believe it has
OL,8,Fspread and I'm taking tests to confirm
OL,9,Ftheir diagnosis.
OL,11,F"So that's it. No chemo. No radiation.
OL,12,FJust chicken soup and I Love Lucy
OL,13,Freruns."
OL,15,FManilow, who is best known for hits
OL,16,Fincluding Copacabana, Mandy and Looks
OL,17,FLike We Made It, said he will need to
OL,18,Fspend a month recovering.
