OL,5,Cdiagnosis
OL,7,FThe post noted that ticket holders for
OL,8,Fthe January concerts will be able to
OL,9,Fuse their existing tickets for the
OL,10,Frescheduld dates.
OL,12,FManilow said he is "counting down the
OL,13,Fdays" until his concerts on Valentine
OL,14,FDay weekend in February and throughout
OL,15,F2026 at the Westgate Las Vegas.
OL,17,FHe ended the post advising his 114,000
OL,18,Ffollowers to look after their health,
OL,19,Fstating: "Remember, if you have even
OL,20,Fthe slightest symptom...get tested!"
